\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 11. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 I have lost my first-created beauty and comeliness; and now I lie naked, and I am ashamed. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
