\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 15. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 I have stained the coat of my flesh, and soiled what is in Thy image and likeness, O Savior. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
