ear! But you neither care nor prepare. The time is growing short. Rise! The Judge is near at the very doors. Like a dream, like a flower, the time of this life passes. Why do we bustle about in vain? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 (Matthew 24:33; Psalm 38:7)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12938973 
