\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 4. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 There has never been a sin or act or vice in life that I have not committe
d, O Savior. I have sinned in mind, word and choice, in purpose, will and action, as no one else has ever done. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12938973 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 5. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 
Therefore I am condemned, wretch that I am, therefore I am doomed by my own conscience, than which there is nothing in the world more rigorous. O my Judge and Redeemer Who knowest my heart, spare and deliver and save me, Thy servant. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12938973 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 6. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 
The ladder of old which the great Patriarch saw, my soul, is a model of mounting by action and ascent by knowledge. So, if you wish to live in activity, knowledge and contemplation, be renewed. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 
