\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 7. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 Because of his cr
ying need the Patriarch endured the scorching heat of the day, and he bore the frost of the night, daily making gains, shepherding, struggling, slaving, in order to win two wives. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 
