\insrsid12938973 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 9. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 Watch, my soul! Be courageous like th
e great Patriarchs, that you may acquire activity and awareness, and be a mind that sees God, and may reach in contemplation the innermost darkness, and be a great trader. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 
(Genesis 32:28; Luke 19:13. -15) }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12938973 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs38\f1\fs16\insrsid12938973 10. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs37\f1\fs32\insrsid12938973 The great Patriarch, by begetting the twelve 
